Start MongoDB Shell
mongosh

Show All Databases
show dbs

Create or Switch to a Database
use studentDB

Check Current Database
db

Show All Collections (Tables)
show collections

Create a Collection (Optional)
db.createCollection("students")

Insert Data
db.students.insertOne({ name: "Swaraj", marks: 90, city: "Pune" })

View All Documents
db.students.find().pretty()

Continue Working With Previous Database
use studentDB

Delete a Collection
db.students.drop()

Delete a Database
db.dropDatabase()

Helpful Info Commands
db.stats()        // Shows stats of current DB
db.students.countDocuments()  // Counts all documents
db.students.findOne()         // Shows a single document
